Title: The Choice (Nicholas Sparks 2016 Movie) – Official Teaser Trailer
Comment:
I wonder when will people who make trailers learn that they shouldn't show scenes from the entire movie! Show just the beginning so you would intrigue us. Don't show us everything because it won't be interesting to watch! I have stopped watching trailers because of this and I sometimes go back to check if they have made a terrible trailer again, and of course they did. Sadness. 

As for the movie, it was good and I hope that I will meet someone who will treat me the way Trevis treated Gabby. <3 :) I loved how the movie made me feel relaxed, and showed how we all need just a little bit to be happy: someone by our side who will do fun things with us and make us feel loved. 

SPOILER ALERT! 
I need to say few more words about the trailer to people who made it. You could've shown that scene where they met, and then a little bit from when he was flirting with her, and the part where she says that she has a boyfriend. Then you could've ended it with that scene where Travis asks Gabby if she's going to tell her boyfriend about them, and her saying "I don't know". That would be enough. Thank you.

nobody is glorifying cheating... Gabby's relationship with her boyfriend barely existed since she moved to a small town to be close to Kevin (in the movies case Ryan) she always felt like something was missing and that Kevin always avoided talking about their future and being more with gabby (like moving in together, or getting engaged)
